@lynzskate @deena_214 @tim.gately @jasonmveilleux @pit_viper #iwesrsunglassesatnight

node.text:
Spent the week here in Minnesota building the track for round two of the championship. Amazing working with @andrewcarlson15 and crew. The track has so much elevation change, huge banks and zer-gravity drops. It’s windy and going to race really well. Almost no dust and great dirt here but we are intentionally not watering a few of the corners to see if the swept line could be a potential solution for other tracks where the soil blue grooves right away. Happy to get some laps on the CanAm to confirm the jumps are super smooth and will be easy on the cars.
@scott_speed @nitrocircus @yokohamatire @redbullmotorsports

node.text: @matt_crafton and his family came over to drive the @canamoffroad vehicles around the house. Good family fun. #igotfullcoverage 😂 Thanks for all the help and filming a few clips for us @nitrorednekhubert .. Crafton was the first one in a year to break one of these which is very impressive. Can Am’s are are tough as they come. Also, to be fair to Matt, it was pretty bent from @conordaly22 last cartwheel which I’m sure contributed 🤔🤦👍

node.text:
The Subaru #airslayer is an absolute beast. Crushed the previous record of 5:44.2 (@nitrorallycross subaru) and turned in a 5:28.6. Huge thanks to @yokohamatire for helping with a tire that didn’t fade even with all four wheels digging and sliding all the way to the top.  The crew at @subarumotorsportsusa @vermont.sportscar .. thank you for building the scariest / most fun weapon of a vehicle imaginable for @mtwashautoroad .. #hellofaride #madeit 
@kmcwheels @alpinestars

node.text:
Got two practice runs on the top half of Mt Washington today in the gymkhana airslayer STI. What a ride! Hopefully weather holds up for tomorrow’s runs on the bottom half and for the official full run of the 2021 #climbtotheclouds hillclimb this Sunday. 
@subarumotorsportsusa @yokohamatire @kmcwheels @alpinestars

node.text:
The @mtwashautoroad available to drive now on @iracingofficial !! You can Drive the Subaru I set the record with in 2017 and see if you can beat my real life time on your sim. Then try again Sunday and compare against my time in the air slayer STI. More of the road was paved since 2017 so it should be faster (and my car is faster). With any luck, we will have some@great weather to make a clean run.
@subarumotorsportsusa @subaru_usa @yokohamatire @redbullmotorsports @alpinestars
